00:09:13.860 --> 00:09:15.860
Well, what's the point?

00:09:15.860 --> 00:09:17.860
We don't want to wait that long, of course.

00:09:17.860 --> 00:09:22.860
But even an awkward attempt at expressing affection in our family

00:09:22.860 --> 00:09:24.860
is an act of love,

00:09:24.860 --> 00:09:27.860
and it can do so much good.

00:09:27.860 --> 00:09:30.860
That's a habit we all want to cultivate.

00:09:30.860 --> 00:09:32.860
Let's consider a second habit.

00:09:32.860 --> 00:09:38.860
Be kind in your actions, tone of voice, and choice of words.

00:09:38.860 --> 00:09:42.860
In the video, we recall Irene's reassurance to her daughter, Olivia.

00:09:42.860 --> 00:09:45.860
