00:10:12.860 --> 00:10:14.860
Well, that's in the past.

00:10:14.860 --> 00:10:17.860
But what can we all do now?

00:10:17.860 --> 00:10:22.860
We can pray to Jehovah to help us take the lead in showing kindness.

00:10:23.860 --> 00:10:26.860
For example, every day greeting one another kindly.

00:10:26.860 --> 00:10:29.860
Every day, saying, please, and thank you,

00:10:29.860 --> 00:10:33.860
sharing little gifts, making time to talk, really listening.

00:10:33.860 --> 00:10:37.860
All of these are acts of kindness.

00:10:37.860 --> 00:10:41.860
That's a good habit we all want to cultivate.

00:10:41.860 --> 00:10:43.860
What's habit number three?

00:10:43.860 --> 00:10:48.860
Be quick to apologize and forgive freely.

00:10:48.860 --> 00:10:52.860
In the video, Olivia's new step-sister Sue apologized

00:10:52.860 --> 00:10:55.860
